column4:
To keep yourself &amp; others safe while food shopping during the #COVID19 pandemic:

• Wear a face covering or mask while shopping;
• Wash your reusable bags before each use; 
• Practice social distancing while shopping.

Check out @USDA's useful guide: https://t.co/E54dBOQg5D

I just voted in support of critical #covid19 legislation that ensures we are putting the needs of #FamiliesFirst:

*securing free #covid19 testing for all;
* ensuring paid leave for employees;
* increasing federal funds for Medicaid; and
*strengthening meal assistance programs.
